{"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layout to add in your views a lonely checkbox, without labels, texts nor icons components."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a checkbox with additional texts and icon, prefer instead "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents25OUDSCheckboxIndeterminateV","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate"}],"title":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","roleHeading":"Structure","symbolKind":"struct","role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"kind":"symbol","relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Indicator states","level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"indeterminate"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": like a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In you are looking for a checkbox with only two possible values, refer to ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Particular cases","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Accessibility considerations","level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Cases forbidden by design","level":2,"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Code samples","level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Suggestions","level":2,"anchor":"Suggestions"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/09d860-checkbox\/t\/14bf4bd854","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"w"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Design documentation","level":2,"anchor